                    <ab>Venditio plurium <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terrarum</rs> cum <rs
                            key="#Cereals">campis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Forests">silvisque</rs>, facta a <persName key="#householdOf"
                                ><name ref="Bogallo">Bogallo</name></persName> cum consensu
                            <persName key="#dominus/seniorOf"><name ref="Amelricus"
                            >Almerici</name></persName> patroni sui, ex hereditate patris et matris
                        suê, favore <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName> fil… Actum
                        in <rs key="#Burgi">burgo</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/80" key="#Burgi">Ferrariê</placeName>. Rog. … Anno
                        domini <persName key="#Popes" ref="#people/1572">Iohannis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Popes">papê</rs> … <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/130"
                            >Henrici II</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">regis</rs> IV, indictione VI, 26 decembris.</ab>
                </div>
